e 個d幾分鐘帶氧運動<br />\nGym 未必會教你<br />\n因為屋企都做到 但係其實body weight個難度其實都唔低<br />\n<br />\n手臂同大脾同body weight 已經夠<br />\n做push up 同squat jump 可以修到線條好好<br />\n而且同時會用到全身肌肉<br />\n個線條會比較自然<br />\n<br />\n背肌係好重要唔好<br />\n要企得直 胸部腰部線條先可以特出到"},{"pid":"5cbab61d6fe3a4de2c2d7192a9bbbacc2f614cdf","tid":733394,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e1334c1cdc04d025a4a618d9de84544f9658f20","tid":733394,"uid":174688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cda6905ce7b6fa36717daea82e56a30f08564a4b","tid":733394,"uid":125590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ba791531dfc9a97a6e724e428229514280fd40d","tid":733394,"uid":174688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T02:57:00.000Z","msg":"終於有人覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝師姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果帶氧唔係做跑步 滑雪，<br />\n仲有邊種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好奇問 <br />\n點解body weight exercise 會仲快見效過做機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身以為做機做重啲就可以幫到firm返啲拜拜肉 ，所以join左會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見啲sales都係話咩都唔好練，<br />\n淨係練左背肌先，<br />\n咁即係做機只做背肌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁手臂同大脾做body weight就夠 ?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"repl